STYLES

- there are 3 ways to apply styles to the component:
    1) using styleUrls in the component meta data to specify the path of style.
        styleUrl: './favourite.component.css',
    2) using styles property in the component meta data to write inline styles.
        styles: [
            '
            //
            '
        ]
    3) writing the styles inline in our html template 
        (favourite.component.html)
        <style>
            //
        </style>
        <button [style.backgroundColor]="isFavourite ? 'green' : 'white'" (click)="toggleFavourite()">Input Prop</button>
        //


- for the purpose of finding out style overwrite.
    1) styleUrl = red
    2) style = green
    3) html template style = blue

    -> method 3) always overwrites methods 1) and 2).
    -> between methods 1) and 2), 2) overwrite 1).
       